  "image_directives": "soft, naturally lit yoga photography. Real students mid-flow, blanketed savasana, props like bolsters and cork blocks visible. Diverse bodies and ages, modest mat-side framing. Avoid airbrushed studio-model poses on cliff edges, no incense smoke clichés, no cultural costume shots. Wood floors, plants, daylight through linen curtains. Hands adjusting safely, eyes closed in seated breath, not fashion-shoot arches.",
